  "text": "Behavioural observations were conducted in four strategically selected locations ( The observations were conducted during four weeks period in Jun 2017 and comprise both weekdays and weekends. The direct and counting observations occurred in 15min counting sessions followed with 15min direct observation sessions to capture both peak and after peak activities following the adapted approach by Jan Gehl [CITATION_1] . All the results are represented through maps, demonstrating not only a visualising tool, but a tool that enables comparison of results.",
